84
00:04:20.360 --> 00:04:22.330
Don't get all high and mighty with me!

85
00:04:22.740 --> 00:04:25.200
They won't surrender.

86
00:04:25.200 --> 00:04:26.870
Those are the Straw Hat Pirates.

87
00:04:26.870 --> 00:04:29.000
Their captain was just named an Emperor.

88
00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:30.250
I know, right?!

89
00:04:31.420 --> 00:04:34.750
An Emperor must be rolling in treasure!

90
00:04:35.340 --> 00:04:37.720
In that case, you've made a grave error.

91
00:04:38.840 --> 00:04:39.680
An error?

92
00:04:40.050 --> 00:04:42.430
