No, you underestimated them.

95
00:04:46.470 --> 00:04:48.890
Look at the swordsman on the ship.

96
00:04:49.560 --> 00:04:56.030
That's Pirate Hunter Zoro,
a man worth 1 billion 111 million berries.

97
00:04:56.030 --> 00:05:01.490
He's calm because he knows he can
kill you in an instant from there.

98
00:05:02.320 --> 00:05:06.160
Same goes for the woman behind him, 
Devil Child Nico Robin.

99
00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:10.500
